### Step 3 — Fix `JwtTokenBuilder.AddClaims` bug
**File:** `src/MagiqAuth.Web/Api/v1/Models/Security/JwtTokenBuilder.cs`

```csharp
// Before (no-op):
this.claims.Union(claims);

// After:
foreach (var kvp in claims)
    this.claims[kvp.Key] = kvp.Value;
```

